references: Related: CF 281909, CF 272833, CF 281909. Amending: Ord 101234, Ord 104505
summary: AN ORDINANCE amending Section 1 of Ordinance 101234 providing for the planting of street trees on Rainier Avenue South to further extend the scope of the project, increase the amount of the appropriation from the Arterial Development Fund and authorize an agreement with the State of Washington, Washington State Highway Commission for partial reimbursement.
